AzureBlade opens his wings and lifts from the ground. He faces the Maximal 
base.

AzureBlade:
Greetings, Cindro. My name is AzureBlade and I desire to become once again a 
member of the Maximals. I would like to meet your leader, if you are not the 
leader yourself. I have a history to deal with, and I wish to know if your 
group can appreciate my abilities through it.

He then waved a hand towards the newcomers that had been waiting with him.

AzureBlade:
I guess my other companions here have motives other than mines to join up, 
so I will let them speak.
